Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮諾  男人只要抓住了他的胃袋就萬事OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要像挖坑一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挖坑一樣
